                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Shield of Forgetfulness:
<br />
How about a damage shield type buff that affects hate instead of doing damage?  Each time you get hit, it has a boggle-type affect which reduces the mobs aggro, making it less likely to hit you again.  Single target, but targetable - make it last 10 mins and refresh in 15.
<br />

<br />
Theft of Magic:
<br />
Recant type dispell that gives the enchanter mana equal to the casting cost of the buffs/debuffs that it dispells.
<br />

<br />
Group Rune
<br />
Make our single target non-self only runes groupable.
<br />

<br />
and one just for fun:
<br />

<br />
Purple:
<br />
Turn target purple - Literally change tinting so the target is purple for a fixed duration.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
