                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">...whether a single BIG AA, or one with several levels, this is one I want.
<br />

<br />
It should double the size of the dmage absorption of all runes cast, and allow for a hotkey to make the next rune (other than self-only) cast a group cast for double the component cost (or 4 times for a MGB).  If they want to make it several levels, then how about scaling the increase in rune absorption up to double, and adding little perks like increased dodge, mana regen, and mitigation, along with the hotkey for making a single target rune a group one.
<br />

<br />
THAT is one I would willingly pay 20 AA (or 5/10/15) for!
