                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Two things:
<br />

<br />
In terms of new AA.
<br />

<br />
1)  Innate Tashania 
<br />
Every enchanter always has some version of Tash loaded, and innate tash would fix the spell refresh problem and give us another spell slot.
<br />

<br />
2)  More spell gems
<br />
Eight was hardly enough in Velious.  With all the new spell lines, how about changing that hardcoded 8 to 12 or 16?   Charge us AA but give us flexibility.
<br />

<br />
3)  Improved Eldritch Rune
<br />
Lower the refresh timer of ER.  Three ranks, 10 percent per rank.
<br />

<br />
*edit: forgot one*
<br />
4)  Mana Arbitration
<br />
Start at 25 pecent penalty, be able to buy it down to 10.  Work like Divine Arbitration.  Give it a five or ten minute refresh.
<br />

<br />
or
<br />

<br />
5)  Hand of Piety type mana effect
<br />
15-30 minute refresh.   4-600 mana restored to every member of group.
<br />

<br />
In terms of our nukes having a long recast.    This was because enchanter nukes all used to have a stun component.  All stuns have a long refresh to prevent chain stunning with a single nuke.   
<br />

<br />
Now that the enchanter nukes don't stun, how about removing the long refresh timer?  It sucks having to alternative my mana preserved nuke with dementing visions.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=346799" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Saedaar</a>
<br />
Epic Coercer of Tunare
<br />
