                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I like the idea of some "Innate" hot keyed spells to represent enchanters are the true masters of mezing, dispelling, lowering MR, Mem Bluring.  This is mostly to save me from having to swap out spells or always having to devote a slot to it.
