                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">First off i would LOVE to have the "fading memory" or "SoS" type i mean we are the masters of illusion(although anyone can be now with those damn pots and masks) no reason we shouldn't be able to blend in with the surroundings and "escape" from battle because again we got the memory blur and mind control that other classes don't get.  Consider it our minor illusion upgrade  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_dance.gif" alt="eusa_dance.gif" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Second, i want the AE mana that is like the cleric druid AE heal and even though bards are taking our job since they can get more mana regen out then we can.  We already got ways to get our mana back why not give it in AE form.
<br />

<br />
Third i want to see something like mana shield that would be sweet once you get hit so much.....say to 20m.......it goes back to taking hp would help survivability.  
<br />

<br />
Forth although i would like a targetable gather mana thing.  I see its usefulness but im mixed on it.  It would evolve to like necros that don't want to twitch.
<br />

<br />
Fifth, i would like to see something that makes our mez unresistable or just have it a hotkey that would us it as such.  You got 4 things you insta mez one thats flagged mezzable without worry and then single the rest.  As long as its a good time/reuse time it wont get abused.
<br />

<br />
Sixth, with mobs starting to hit for 3k really need some defensive type here like the melees got.  Say spell casting takes 1.5x longer to cast but you take less dmg.  Or you can have a better rune altho sometimes i die so fast that i don't really get a chance to use it.  Or you can make like you are snared but you take half dmg.  Now i don't think thats to hard to give to us i mean chanters are gettin hit just as much as tanks when we have to do mass CC like in uqua or some of this Txevu things.
<br />

<br />
Those just what i can think of right now im sure there are tons more.  As longs as they are useful i wont mind much but 3/4 of our GoD AA's are really useless.
<br />

<br />
--------Shalow on Vazaelle----------
